<lb ed="C I" n="0147b01"/>大齊天保五年歲次甲戌四月丙辰朔
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b02"/>二日丁巳。　天宮頌<app source="0147004" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">文</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08387;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b03"/>夫<note n="0147005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30833;＝至【史語所】</note><app n="0147005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">至</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30833;</rdg></app>道沖靜。必資物以顯真。沈隱留像。
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b04"/>因阿難以存形。須達捨金。感群迷以就
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b05"/>正。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">是</unclear>以邑儀人等。故知大慈異興。<note n="0147006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03850;＝閻【史語所】</note><app n="0147006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">閻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03850;</rdg></app>浮
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b06"/>難<note n="0147007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB20060;＝處【史語所】</note><app n="0147007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB20060;</rdg></app>。磬竭家珍。敬崇三寶。造二寶塔。石
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b07"/>像三區。上為　皇帝<note n="0147008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30834;＝永【史語所】</note><app n="0147008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">永</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30834;</rdg></app>隆。百官朝慶。法
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b08"/>　界有形。咸同斯<note n="0147009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30779;＝願【史語所】</note><app n="0147009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30779;</rdg></app>。其詞曰　金柱一
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b09"/>振。万侶俱張。同茲<app source="0147002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30838;</rdg></app>法。眾惠旡常。一階
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b10"/>超九。<app source="0147008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史語所】">永</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30834;</rdg></app>誤時亡。殊山寶石。異想神功。誤
<lb ed="C I" n="0147b11"/>斯應狀。動現真容。虛來異顯。滅去難蹤。
